  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But what I did there was obviously against-- or what I participated in-- was obviously against their national interest, and so it would have been very easy for them to say, well, sorry, Joe, but you know, you've shown us your colors once.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We don't particularly want to accept you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think that's the greatness in the British system.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "However much we sort of criticize it at times-- there's a lot, unfortunately, nowadays to be criticized-- there comes out the greatness of this nation, I think.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I would like this to be-- that's why I mentioned it-- I would like that to be recorded, I think, out of fairness, yes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, another tape.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
